            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">普通攻击</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理伤害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/16/157749474/94aa30ae75b8c7c6a9c64ab05bd5dda7_4536782337368991702.png",
                "id": "talent30617",
                "key": "弦月舞步",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "弦月舞步"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素战技</span></p><p>造成3点<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素伤害</span>，如果队伍中包含<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素角色</span>和<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素角色</span>且不包含其他元素的角色，就生成<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">金杯的丰馈</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/16/157749474/c82a120ef3389c55999b6069de0c8ddc_2864420481884657550.png",
                "id": "talent6219",
                "key": "七域舞步",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "七域舞步"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素伤害</span>，目标角色附属<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">永世流沔</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/16/157749474/e701a5d9dee57abe1f108242af52b000_3192692917946906433.png",
                "id": "talent41499",
                "key": "浮莲舞步 ‧ 远梦聆泉",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "浮莲舞步 ‧ 远梦聆泉"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">召唤物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">结束阶段：</span>造成2点<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素伤害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数：1</span>（可叠加，最多叠加到3次）</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">我方宣布结束时：</span>如果此牌的<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次数</span>至少为2，则造成2点<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素伤害</span>。（需消耗<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/16/157749474/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_5371452042171904235.png",
                "id": "talent88192",
                "key": "丰穰之核",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/16/157749474/ded0956520d3dce12af6dfcbdfab5d01_986132590746082530.png",
                "title": "丰穰之核"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附着水元素，可发生元素反应：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: white\">蒸发</span>：本伤害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: white\">感电</span>：本伤害+1，对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点穿透伤害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: white\">冻结</span>：本伤害+1，使目标本回合无法行动（受到物理或火元素伤害后提前解除，但是伤害+2）</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>】<span style=\"color: white\">绽放</span>：本伤害+1，生成使下次火元素或雷元素伤害+2的[<span style=\"color: white\">草原核</span>]</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/16/157749474/a126c6a302d81c07e19cf9a9f1260f90_7151823288307644412.png",
                "id": "talent25466",
                "key": "水元素伤害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "水元素伤害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">物理伤害</span></strong></p><p>物理伤害不会附着元素，也不会发生元素反应。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">金杯的丰馈</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出战状态</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">敌方角色受到绽放反应时：</span>我方不再生成<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">草原核</span>，而是改为召唤<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">丰穰之核</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">草原核</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出战状态</span></p><p>我方对敌方出战角色造成<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素伤害</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素伤害</span>时，伤害值+2。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数：1</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">可用次数</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果触发后，会消耗1次<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">永世流沔</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">状态</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">结束阶段：</span>对所附属角色造成3点卡牌<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素伤害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数：1</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/16/157749474/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_7981439000301555952.png",
